<div className="logo-page-wrapper">
    # Logos

    The logos are available for download here: [https://design.miljodirektoratet.no/profilbank/miljodirektoratet/logo/](https://design.miljodirektoratet.no/profilbank/miljodirektoratet/logo/)

    **The primary logo should be used whenever possible.**

    Where it is technically difficult to use the primary logo in a way that keeps the text legible, the secondary logo should be used. This applies, for example, when used in narrow formats or together with other logos.

    ## Clear Space

    There must always be sufficient clear space around the logo. The minimum required clear space is defined as the width of the space beneath the “M” symbol in the logo, rounded up to the nearest size within the 8-point scale. The logo may always have more clear space around it than this, but never less. The logo must be placed in a visually calm area.

    ## Minimum Size

    The minimum height of the primary logo is 8 mm. For the secondary logo, the minimum height of the M symbol is 20 mm.

    ----
</div>

    There must always be sufficient clear space around the logo.

    The minimum required clear space is defined as the width of the space beneath the “M” symbol in the logo, rounded up to the nearest size within the 8-point scale. The logo may always have more clear space around it than this, but never less. The logo must be placed in a visually calm area.
